quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  2,84,"aur jab hum ne tum se ehad liya ke aapas mein kasht wa khoon nah karna aur apne ko un ke watan se nah nikalna to tum ne iqraar kar liya, aur tum ( is baat ke ) gawah ho"
  2,85,"phir tum wohi ho ke apnon ko qatal bhi kar dete ho aur apne mein se baaz logon par gunah aur zulm se charhai karkay inhen watan se nikaal bhi dete ho, aur agar woh tumahray paas qaid ho kar ayen to badla day kar un ko churra bhi letay ho, halaank un ka nikaal dena hi tum ko haraam tha. ( yeh )kiya ( baat hai ke ) tum ktabِ ( khuda ) ke baaz ehkaam ko to mantay ho aur baaz se inkaar kiye dete ho, to jo tum mein se aisi harkat karen, un ki saza is ke siwa aurkiya ho sakti hai ke duniya ki zindagi mein to ruswai ho aur qayamat ke din sakht se sakht azaab mein daal diye jayen aur jo kaam tum karte ho, khuda un se ghaafil nahi"
  2,86,yeh woh log hain jinhon ne akhirat ke badlay duniya ki zindagi khareedi. so nah to un se azaab hi halkakiya jaye ga aur nah un ko ( aur terhan ki ) madad miley gi
  2,87,"aur hum ne moose ko kitaab inayat ki aur un ke peechay yakke baad deegray paighambar bhaijtay rahay aur eesa ban maryam ko khulay nishanaat bakhshay aur rooh al quds ( yani jbryil ) se un ko madad di. to jab koi paighambar tumahray paas aisi baatein le kar aeye, jin ko tumhara jee nahi chahta tha, to tum sarkash ho jatay rahay, aur aik giroh ( anbia ) ko to jutlatay rahay aur aik giroh ko qatal karte rahay"
  2,87,( mslmano ) tum par ( khuda ke raste mein ) larna farz kardiya gaya hai woh tumhe nagawaar to hoga magar ajab nahi ke aik cheez tum ko buri lagey aur woh tumahray haq mein bhali ho aur ajab nahi ke aik cheez tum ko bhali lagey aur woh tumahray liye muzir ho. aur un baton ko ) khuda hi behtar jaanta hai aur tum nahi jantay
  2,88,"aur kehte hain, hamaray dil parday mein hain. ( nahi ) balkay allah ne un ke kufar ke sabab un par laanat kar rakhi hai. pas yeh thoray hi par imaan laatay hain"
